                     <h6>NFT for Arts</h6>
                     <p>NFTs have transformed the traditional art market by offering a secure and immutable way to authenticate ownership of digital artwork. Nonfungible tokens allow artists to tokenize their art and sell them as unique, one-of-a-kind digital assets.</p>
                  </div>
