                     <h6>NFT for Music</h6>
                     <p>NFTs have also disrupted the music industry by providing musicians with new ways to monetize their digital content. Musicians can tokenize their music and sell them as unique, collectible assets, allowing them to profit from the appreciation of their work over time.</p>
