                     <h6>NFT for Films</h6>
                     <p>Nfts offer filmmakers and studios an innovative way to make money off of their work while giving fans unique access to behind-the-scenes material, specialized goods, and other experiences. Limited-edition items can be used to authenticate ownership using nonfungible tokens.</p>
