                     <h6>NFT for Fashion</h6>
                     <p>Nonfungible tokens have disrupted the fashion industry by providing a way to authenticate ownership of limited-edition or custom clothing and accessories. NFTs can be used to prove authenticity and ownership and provide collectors with a new way to display and trade their fashion assets. 
                     </p>
