                     <h6>NFT for real estate</h6>
                     <p>Nonfungible tokens can transform the real estate business by enabling a secure and transparent means to purchase, sell, and exchange real estate. Tokenizing real estate assets with NFTs provides a digital representation of ownership that can be bought and traded on secondary markets.</p>
